            ],
            "marks": 4,
            "negMarks": 1,
            "question": {
              "en": {
                "comprehension": null,
                "direction": null,
                "content": "<p>A 40 W electric bulb emits light of wavelength 620 nm and works with 80% efficiency. Find the number of photons emitted by the bulb in 20 seconds. (1 eV = $1.6 \\times 10^{-19}$ J, $hc = 12400$ eV &Aring;)</p>",
                "options": [
                  {
                    "identifier": "A",
                    "content": "<p>$2 \\times 10^{18}$</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "B",
                    "content": "<p>$10^{18}$</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "C",
                    "content": "<p>$10^{21}$</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "D",
                    "content": "<p>$2 \\times 10^{21}$</p>"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "hi": {
                "comprehension": null,
                "direction": null,
                "content": "<p>एक 40 W का विद्युत बल्ब 620 nm तरंगदैर्घ्य का प्रकाश उत्सर्जित करता है और 80% दक्षता के साथ कार्य करता है। 20 सेकंड में बल्ब द्वारा उत्सर्जित फोटॉनों की संख्या ज्ञात कीजिए। (1 eV = $1.6 \\times 10^{-19}$ J, $hc = 12400$ eV &Aring;)</p>",
                "options": [
                  {
                    "identifier": "A",
                    "content": "<p>$2 \\times 10^{18}$</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "B",
                    "content": "<p>$10^{18}$</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "C",
                    "content": "<p>$10^{21}$</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "D",
                    "content": "<p>$2 \\times 10^{21}$</p>"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "subTopic": null,
            "subject": "chemistry",
            "timeAllotted": 90000,
            "topic": "photoelectric-effect",
            "type": "mcq"
          },
          {
            "questionId": "tq-mpzvbbl2",
            "chapter": "structure-of-atom",
            "chapterGroup": "physical-chemistry",
            "country": "in",
            "difficulty": "easy",
            "exam": "jee-main",
            "examGroup": "jee",
            "languages": [
              "en"
            ],
            "marks": 4,
            "negMarks": 1,
            "question": {
              "en": {
                "comprehension": null,
                "direction": null,
                "content": "<p>Consider two atoms represented as $z_1A^{M_1}$ and $z_2B^{M_2}$. Given that $M_1 \\neq M_2$ and $Z_1 \\neq Z_2$, but the difference $(M_1 - Z_1)$ is equal to $(M_2 - Z_2)$, these two species are classified as</p>",
                "options": [
                  {
                    "identifier": "A",
                    "content": "<p>Isotones</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "B",
                    "content": "<p>Isobars</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "C",
                    "content": "<p>Isotopes</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "D",
                    "content": "<p>Isoprotonic</p>"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "hi": {
                "comprehension": null,
                "direction": null,
                "content": "<p>मान लीजिए कि दो परमाणुओं को $z_1A^{M_1}$ और $z_2B^{M_2}$ के रूप में दर्शाया गया है। दिया गया है कि $M_1 \neq M_2$ और $Z_1 \neq Z_2$ है, लेकिन अंतर $(M_1 - Z_1)$, $(M_2 - Z_2)$ के बराबर है, तो इन दोनों स्पीशीज़ को किस रूप में वर्गीकृत किया जाता है?</p>",
                "options": [
                  {
                    "identifier": "A",
                    "content": "<p>समन्यूट्रॉनिक (Isotones)</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "B",
                    "content": "<p>समभारिक (Isobars)</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "C",
                    "content": "<p>समस्थानिक (Isotopes)</p>"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "D",
                    "content": "<p>समप्रोटॉनिक (Isoprotonic)</p>"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "subTopic": null,
            "subject": "chemistry",
            "timeAllotted": 90000,
            "topic": "quantum-mechanical-model-of-atom",
            "type": "mcq"
          },
          {
            "questionId": "tq-mpzw3kh3",
            "chapter": "structure-of-atom",
            "chapterGroup": "physical-chemistry",
            "country": "in",
            "difficulty": "easy",
            "exam": "jee-main",
            "examGroup": "jee",
